---
title: Italian Herb Bacon, Leek & Mushroom Fusilli with Garden Salad & Parmesan
description: Twirly-wirly pasta mixed in a creamy sauce is too good to be true. There’s plenty of veggies hidden in amongst the
fusilli to keeps things fresh and green. For a bit of fun, throw in some diced bacon and mushrooms and you’ve cooked
another pasta winning dinner.
